=== Etymology ===

From an unused root meaning to sever; 
=== Noun ===
a bisection, that is, (by implication) the centre: - [[among]] (-st), X between, half, X (there-, where-) in (-to), middle, mid [-night], midst (among), X out (of), X through, X with (-in).